OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1776881466
OL,3,CThree stowaway bunnies found hiding on
OL,4,CNorth Sea rig
OL,6,FThree stowaway bunnies have been
OL,7,Frescued after being found on a
OL,8,Fdrilling rig in the middle of the
OL,9,FNorth Sea.
OL,11,FThe bunnies were discovered on the
OL,12,FValaris Norway rig at a gas field more
OL,13,Fthan 90 miles off the Lincolnshire
OL,14,Fcoast.
OL,16,FIt's believed that the animals had
OL,17,Ffound a warm hiding place inside a
OL,18,Fshipping container in Dundee before
OL,19,Feventually ending up on the rig, where
OL,20,Ftwo were spotted hopping around the
OL,21,Fdeck.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
