OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1776881466
OL,3,CThree stowaway bunnies found hiding on
OL,4,CNorth Sea rig
OL,6,FThe two bunnies were caught by the
OL,7,Fcrew who kept them safe in the radio
OL,8,Froom. They were then transported by
OL,9,Fboat back to Aberdeen where they were
OL,10,Fhanded to an animal rescue charity.
OL,12,FA third bunny was later found hiding
OL,13,Fin a forklift pocket but has now been
OL,14,Fsafely reunited with its siblings at
OL,15,Fthe New Arc animal rescue, near Ellon.
OL,17,FPaul Reynolds, co-manager of the
OL,18,Frescue, said the bunnies were all
OL,19,Fdoing well.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1776881466
OL,3,CThree stowaway bunnies found hiding on
OL,4,CNorth Sea rig
OL,6,F"They are all gaining weight and doing
OL,7,Feverything we'd expect to see with
OL,8,Fhealthy wild rabbits. That includes
OL,9,Ftucking into native leafy greens and
OL,10,Fplants."
OL,12,FMr Reynolds said rabbits had been well
OL,13,Flooked after on board.
OL,15,F"The crew did a very good job of
OL,16,Fcapturing the rabbits, getting them
OL,17,Finto a container and providing
OL,18,Fvegetables and water and it seems to
OL,19,Fhave worked," he said.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1776881466
OL,3,CThree stowaway bunnies found hiding on
OL,4,CNorth Sea rig
OL,6,F"When they arrived they'd (the
OL,7,Frabbits) clearly been eating and they
OL,8,Fwere not particularly stressed so they
OL,9,Fdid a very good job."
OL,11,FHe added: "Out at sea on a rig it's
OL,12,Fnot exactly the environment where
OL,13,Ftaking care of wild animals is going
OL,14,Fto be easy. They don't have access to
OL,15,Fanything apart from what they have in
OL,16,Fthe human kitchen but they did a very
OL,17,Fgood job."
